Being unaware of one’s health, be it physical or mental, has become the biggest threat to human beings today.

इसमें एक और मजेदार परत जोड़ते हैं, हिंदी में एक टिप्पणी छोड़ें और हम सभी गुप्त क्लब में एक-दूसरे को पहचान सकते हैं।

videos.title: Guess Where I'm Going...
videos.description:
Want to be a Stream Clipper for LeeThe4th and get access to an exclusive community? The community of a stream/video clippers involves watching LeeThe4th's streams or videos, capturing the funniest and most exciting moments, and sharing them on social media. Clip streamers need to post at least 3 clips daily to be part of the team and can earn rewards based on the total views their clips receive. 

How to Become a Stream Clipper for LeeThe4th:
Create an Account: Make a new social media account (or use an old one you don't use anymore).

Watch the Videos: Tune into LeeThe4th’s streams or YouTube videos and look for the funniest, coolest, or craziest moments!

Record the Best Parts: Use your phone's screen recording:

iPhone/iPad: Swipe down, press the record button.
Android: Use a screen recording app.
Need help? Search Videos on Youtube
Cut the Clip: Use free apps like CapCut or InShot to trim the video (10-60 seconds) and add text or emojis if you want!

Post Your Clip: Share your clip on social media with #LeeThe4thClips and #LeeThe4th, then tag @LeeThe4th.

Post 3 Clips Daily: You MUST post 3 clips every day to be part of the team!

Earn Rewards:
Rewards:
25,000 Views: Get a follow back from Lee!
100,000 Views: Get a shoutout on Lee's live stream!
1 Million Views: Get into an exclusive Discord group to chat with Lee and other clippers!
Tools to Use: CapCut, InShot, and screen recording on your phone.

Start now and have fun! 🎥👑

How to Become a Stream Clipper for LeeThe4th:
Create an Account: Make a new social media account (or use an old one you don't use anymore).

Watch the Videos: Tune into LeeThe4th’s streams or YouTube videos and look for the funniest, coolest, or craziest moments!

Record the Best Parts: Use your phone's screen recording:

iPhone/iPad: Swipe down, press the record button.
Android: Use a screen recording app.
Need help? Search Videos on Youtube
Cut the Clip: Use free apps like CapCut or InShot to trim the video (10-60 seconds) and add text or emojis if you want!

Post Your Clip: Share your clip on social media with #LeeThe4thClips and #LeeThe4th, then tag @LeeThe4th.

Post 3 Clips Daily: You MUST post 3 clips every day to be part of the team!

Earn Rewards:
Rewards:
25,000 Views: Get a follow back from Lee!
100,000 Views: Get a shoutout on Lee's live stream!
1 Million Views: Get into an exclusive Discord group to chat with Lee and other clippers!
Tools to Use: CapCut, InShot, and screen recording on your phone.

Start now and have fun! 🎥👑

PZ9 and his evil hacker organization have hidden the briefcase at the top of a rock climbing wall since Melvin is the only one who can reach it. Daniel tries to climb to the top but is too scared as he has a fear of heights. So he calls in his ex girlfriend Alie to help him overcome his fear of heights, train, improve his strength and find a way to make it to the top of the climbing wall. Together the train and climb to the top of the wall to press the two-man switch at the same time in order to unlock the secret door that holds the briefcase. They finally unlock the door but  Daniel is met with a huge surprise when he opens the door to find Melvin PZ9 and his evil hackers instead of the  briefcase. Will Daniel be able to escape the evil PZ9 alone?

Vy forgets about the cupcakes and they come out burnt, Daniel and Regina make a pact to kiss on New Years. w/ rain & slowed

song story by Isaac dunbar *PLEASE READ*:
"i just wanna say i wrote this song for those who feel alone. i’ve had one of my best friends attempt suicide three times and i wrote this song as a gift to her. i was there by her hospital bed for hours with her, and i wrote this song to comfort her. to know that i care and that i love her. reading all these comments and seeing how this song is comforting people is insanely surreal, and my i’m so grateful that my goal has been achieved. 

this song is a gift to anyone who struggles with suicidal thoughts.. feeling as if you’re alone and that nobody cares about you... you are NOT alone. don’t ever give up"

1-800-273-8255
https://suicidepreventionlifeline.org

Jesus loves you.

videos.title: #MiCorazoncito #Aventura #SanValentín #tuex
videos.description: "Mi Corazoncito" by Aventura is a beloved bachata classic that captures the essence of romantic longing and passion. With its infectious rhythm, soulful vocals by Romeo Santos, and heartfelt lyrics, the song enchants listeners, inviting them to sway to its irresistible beat and immerse themselves in its heartfelt emotion. It's a timeless anthem of love and desire that has cemented Aventura's place as one of the most iconic groups in bachata music.
videos.author: Aventura

videos.title: #DileAlAmor #IdontneednoLoveinmyLife #Aventura #valentinesday Valentine
videos.description:
"Dile Al Amor" de Aventura es un éxito de bachata que encabeza las listas de éxitos y que muestra la combinación característica del grupo de lirismo romántico y ritmos contagiosos. Dirigida por la emotiva voz de Romeo Santos, la canción captura la esencia de las complejidades del amor con su melodía sincera y su narración cautivadora. Es un himno atemporal que ha resonado en el público de todo el mundo, solidificando el estatus de Aventura como pioneros de la música bachata moderna.

"Dile Al Amor" by Aventura is a chart-topping bachata hit that showcases the group's signature blend of romantic lyricism and infectious rhythms. Led by Romeo Santos's emotive vocals, the song captures the essence of love's complexities with its heartfelt melody and captivating storytelling. It's a timeless anthem that has resonated with audiences worldwide, solidifying Aventura's status as pioneers of modern bachata music.

#aventura #Dilealamor

Alongside them are popular YouTubers & creators such as Tana Mongeau, H3H3, Mike Majlak, Alex Botez, Cash & Maverick Baker, Ashley Nocera, CJ So Cool, Hayes Grier, Sofie Dossi, Marc D’Amelio, Frazier Kay, and Zach Choi.

Standing in their way are former CPT Champions including Nemo, Princess Love, Maria Ho, Wolfgang, Bryce Hall, Lena Ayad, and Vegas Matt who are all eagerly pursuing their second CPT title.

Welcome to our YouTube channel! I am a proud mom of two sets of twins, and here you'll find a glimpse into my daily life filled with laughter, challenges, and lots of fun. 🌟👩‍👧‍👦👩‍👧‍👦

From sharing my parenting tips and tricks to documenting my kids' hilarious moments and challenges.Get ready for an abundance of laughter, heartwarming moments, and plenty of humor. 😄🎉🤣

In addition to our YouTube adventures, we have also launched our very own family matching clothing brand called TWINSIES. Visit our website annatwinsies.com to explore the vibrant and stylish collections that are perfect for creating memorable family moments. 💖👕👖

So, whether you're a parent, a fellow multiple set of twins family, or simply someone who enjoys a good laugh, subscribe to our channel and join us on this incredible journey. Don't forget to check out TWINSIES for some trendy and adorable matching outfits for your whole family. Let's create cherished memories together!  🎥👪🚀🔥👗👨‍👩‍👧‍👦📸

videos.title: Twins in Mismatched Costumes: A Spooktacular Trick or Treat Adventure! 👻🎃✨
videos.description:
Come along with us on our awesome Trick or Treat adventure in the neighborhood! In this video, we’re exploring houses decked out with spooky decorations, from creepy cobwebs to glowing jack-o'-lanterns. The kids are in their mismatched costumes, ready to collect as much candy as they can!

As we knock on doors, we’re greeted by friendly neighbors who have the best treats waiting for us! You'll see the excitement on the kids' faces as they fill their bags with all sorts of goodies. The streets are alive with laughter and fun, and we even spot some other kids showing off their cool costumes.

Don’t miss out on all the fun as we visit different houses and soak in the Halloween spirit! Stick around until the end to see our epic candy haul and hear about our favorite moments from this spooktacular night! 👻🎃✨

#halloween #trickortreat #familyfun #twins

Get ready to dance and sing along to our latest music video, "Where Are Our Twinsies?" Join Mommy Anna, Daddy Radu, and their adorable 2 sets of twins in this vibrant and playful musical adventure! 🎶✨

In this fun-filled video, watch as kids play with colorful balloons in the front yard, while Mommy Anna brings refreshing drinks and snacks. The excitement escalates when Daddy Radu surprises everyone in a shark costume, leading to hilarious moments and lots of laughter! 🦈🎈

channel.name: Yippee Toys
channel.description:
Welcome to a world of fun videos for toddlers and kids, where toys spark imagination and creativity. Join your favorite characters on exciting adventures filled with playful storytelling and delightful surprises. 

Whether you're here for giggles, discoveries, or just some joyful moments, we’ve got something for every little explorer. Each video is crafted with kids in mind, bringing excitement and fun to their day.

So, hop on board, and don’t forget to hit subscribe to stay updated on all the fun to come!

Thanks for being part of our journey! :)

videos.title: Li'l Woodzeez Farmers Market Truck Toy Playset | Fun Pretend Play for Kids
videos.description: Join us as we unbox and play with the Li'l Woodzeez Farmers Market Truck Toy Playset! In this fun pretend play video, we explore a day in the life of a farmer delivering fresh produce to the local market. Watch as we load up the truck with fruits and veggies and drive around the town, bringing healthy food to everyone!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Intro Video For Yippee Toys
videos.description:
Welcome to our channel, where we create fun and engaging content for kids! Whether you're looking for something exciting to watch or just want to have some fun, we've got it all. From laughs to playful adventures, there's always something exciting waiting for you here.

Join us for lots of fun and laughter! Thanks for watching, and we can’t wait to see you in the next one!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Cooking with a Toy Kitchen | Pretend Play
videos.description: Join us in the kitchen to cook a delicious soup, learn colors, letters, and the alphabet.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Toy Playground Fun | Search for Missing Shapes
videos.description: Watch as a group of friends enjoy their new toy that can transform ordinary objects into something exciting! But when an accident turns the lab into a shapes puzzle, they must work together to find all the missing pieces.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Excavator and Blippi Toys | Pretend Play
videos.description: In this pretend play toy video, Blippi drives his excavator to help his friends dig up fun toys while exploring colors and numbers for a playful learning experience.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Camping Fun with Peppa Pig and Family: Toy Adventure!
videos.description: In this toy pretend play, Peppa's family goes camping, but Daddy Pig brings the wrong items. After helping baby birds, they stay in a cozy cabin, while Daddy enjoys the tent.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Color-Changing Disney Cars Submarine Car Wash Playset
videos.description: Join us as we play with the Submarine Car Wash Disney Pixar Toy Playset, featuring color-changing cars like Lightning McQueen, Mater, Guido, and Storm. Using warm and cold water, watch the cars change colors in this fun pretend play video for kids.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Fun Playtime with Toys
videos.description: Join us for a fun adventure where kids can learn colors while playing with their favorite toys including assembling a lego garbage truck! Watch as we explore bright and vibrant colors through exciting playtime activities that make learning fun and engaging for little ones.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Pool & Jet Ski | Pretend Play Beach Cabin Fun
videos.description: A family visits their friends at their new beach cabin. Together, they help set up, find lost letter toys, and enjoy fun activities like riding a jet ski and playing in the pool. This playful pretend video features fun adventures and teamwork.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Toy & Playset Pretend Play Compilation: Fun Alphabet Learning for Kids
videos.description: Enjoy a fun compilation of our videos that can help kids learn the alphabet. Join Peppa Pig and George as they recover stolen ABC cookies, explore Gabby’s Dollhouse, and learn with toys like Play-Doh, Tayo the Little Bus, and more.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Recycle with Garbage Trucks | Toy Video for Kids
videos.description: A group of friends leave a mess at their campsite, but one of them knows exactly how to help! With teamwork, they sort through the trash, recycling, and compost. This simple pretend play video introduces kids to recycling, colors, counting, and more through fun and interactive play.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Grocery Shopping to the Framers Market | Our Video Compilation for Kids
videos.description: This video compilation features playful adventures, including shopping and fun activities.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Bluey’s Big Moving Day | Pretend Play in the New House
videos.description: Bluey and her family move into a new house, and with your help, they unpack and set up their home. Bluey and Bingo play a fun game while a neighbor family visits to welcome their new neighbors. This is an interactive pretend play video for kids.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Musical Train Playset for Kids | Pretend Play Toy Video
videos.description: Today we have a new playset to play with. Let's put it together and watch the engine go. The entire goes on a train ride.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Peppa's Silly Snow Day | Toy Pretend Play
videos.description: Peppa Pig and George have a silly snow day adventure! From swimsuits in the snow to pretending to be dinosaurs, they play, smash snow forts, and even surf in the snow. This funny pretend play video with toys is perfect for kids who love fun and laughter.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Miss Rabbit's Food Truck Fun! 🍔🌭🍕 | Help Us Cook
videos.description: In this video, we help set up a tiy food truck by cooking delicious items like hamburgers, hot dogs, tacos, pizza, and ice cream. Through fun pretend play, we take and draw customer orders, learning how teamwork makes the job easier and more enjoyable!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Cody’s New Home Adventure! 🏠
videos.description:
Cody moves into a new house and feels a little nervous about making new friends. But don’t worry! His new neighbors, the Cocomelon family, are here to help him settle in. Together, we’ll furnish their rooms and learn the importance of helping friends. 🛋️🏠

Along the way let's learn some big words while having fun with toys and pretend play.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Snow Day Fun with PJ Masks, Peppa Pig and More ❄️⛄ | Pretend Play for Kids
videos.description: In this pretend play video with toys, it’s a snow day, and school is canceled! The kids are excited to build a snowman, but when some troublemakers arrive to spoil their fun, they come up with a clever plan to protect their creation. Along the way, they learn the value of teamwork and friendship while enjoying a fun day in the snow. ❄️⛄
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Farm Fun with Grandparents! 🚜🐮 | Pretend Play with Toys for Kids
videos.description: In this pretend play with toys, the kids visit their grandparents for a fun day at the farm! Together, they help set up a new petting farm playset, and Grandpa takes everyone on a ride in his big tractor. 🚜 Afterward, it's time to feed the animals and find surprise animals hiding inside the barns. 🐔🐷
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: School Adventure! 🚌📚 | Pretend Play with Toys for Kids
videos.description:
Today, a group of friends miss the school bus, so Dad drives them to school. 🚌 Along the way, they pick up more friends and discover a mystery surprise box—who will join them at school?

Once they arrive, they practice counting from 1 to 10, and their teacher helps with spelling and reading. This simple pretend play is a nice way for kids to engage in basic learning while playing with toys.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Peppa Pig’s Pool Party at Gabby’s Dollhouse! 🏊‍♀️🎉 | Funny Pretend Play with Toys for Kids
videos.description:
Peppa Pig is off to a fun pool party at Gabby’s Dollhouse! Gabby just got a brand-new pool delivered, and it’s up to us to help set it up. Once it’s ready, Gabby invites Peppa Pig and George over for some splashy fun. But oh no! Romeo shows up and steals all the water! 😱

Not to worry—Kitty Fairy comes to the rescue! With a little magic, she turns the pool into a ball pit pool. 🎉 Now, Peppa and her friends can have even more fun as surprise guests join the party.

This funny and exciting pretend play with toys video is perfect for kids who love Peppa Pig and Gabby’s Dollhouse!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Peppa Pig Grocery Shopping! 🛒🍎 | Pretend Play for Kids
videos.description: Daddy Pig ate all the food, and now Mommy Pig and Peppa need to go grocery shopping at the farmers market! 🛒🍉 First, we’ll help them make a grocery list. When they arrive, there’s no food—but don’t worry, we’re here to help restock the fruits, vegetables, and other groceries! 🥕🍇
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Gardening and Planting Flowers! 🌻🐝 | Pretend Play
videos.description:
Today, our friends visit their grandparents for a special surprise. They’re planting flowers together! 🌸 While planting, YoYo gets scared when she sees a bee. But Grandma reassures her there’s nothing to fear and explains how bees collect nectar to make honey. 🍯 Soon, butterflies and dragonflies join the fun, making the garden full of new friends!

Let’s learn about flowers and how bees help nature in this fun and pretend play with toys video for kids!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Race Cars Go to the Car Wash! 🚗🧼 | Peppa Pig Pretend Play for Kids
videos.description: Peppa Pig and friends are racing colorful cars, but Night Ninja covers them in sticky splat! 🚗💥 Let’s take the cars to the Disney Pixar submarine car wash with color-changing Lightning McQueen. After a quick wash, they’re ready to race again! 🎉 Perfect for kids who love toy cars, racing, and Peppa Pig!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: George Pig Gets a Thomas and Friends Toy for His Birthday! 🎂🚂 | Pretend Play Video for Kids
videos.description: It’s George Pig’s birthday, and he’s in for a big surprise—he gets a brand new Thomas and Friends toy.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Princess Aurora and Snow White Cook in the Kitchen! 🍰👑 | Pretend Play with Peppa Pig for Kids
videos.description: Princess Aurora and Snow White try baking a cake, but when it doesn’t work out, they head to Yippee Toys restaurant for dessert. 🍪 Peppa Pig takes their order, and we make delicious macaron cookies! 🎉 Join the fun as the Disney Princesses enjoy their treats in this magical pretend play cooking adventure!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Fun on the Playground | Pretend Play for Kids
videos.description: In this pretend play with toys, a little one feels lonely, so their friends are invited for a fun playdate! 🎉 They enjoy a game of hide and seek, play at the playground, and splash in muddy puddles. 🏖️ After getting all messy, it's time for a warm, bubbly bath! 🛁
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Car Adventure on the Race Track! 🚗🎢  and Toy Helicopter 🚁 | Pretend Play
videos.description: In this video, we explore a race track toy where some cars are too big to fit. Using a magical garage playset, we shrink the cars to the right size, allowing them to race on the track. This fun, imaginative play is perfect for toddlers who enjoy vehicles!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Cocomelon Friends Build Vehicles and Race! 🚗🏁 | Fun Video for Kids | Pretend Play with Toys
videos.description: In this video, JJ, YoYo, TomTom, and Cody build vehicles with blocks and then race them on a track they create. It’s all about fun and teamwork as they enjoy playing together. Perfect for kids who love Cocomelon and toy vehicles!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Explore Colors with Cocomelon Toys and Giant Crayons! 🎨🖍️ | Fun Surprises Inside for Kids
videos.description: In this video, we open giant crayons filled with surprise toys! 🖍️ Join our Cocomelon friends as we discover fun toys like Tayo the Little Bus, Play-Doh, and Kinetic Sand.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Learn the Alphabet with Cookie Letters and Toys! 🍪🔤 | Toy Video for Kids
videos.description: Night Ninja and Romeo have stolen Peppa Pig's and George Pig's ABC letter cookies! 🍪 We need to help them find the hidden cookies by exploring Gabby’s Dollhouse and Peppa’s house. Along the way, we’ll learn letters as we search for the missing cookies with Peppa and friends.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Cocomelon Family House Playset! 🏠
videos.description: Today, we’re playing with the Cocomelon family house playset! 🏠 Join JJ and Mommy as they go grocery shopping to buy some healthy snacks. 🛒 Along the way, we’ll learn shapes and colors together with our favorite Cocomelon characters.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Disney Princess Dresses! 👗✨ | Dress Up for the Castle Ball | Pretend Play for Kids
videos.description:
In this video, the Disney Princesses are invited to Queen Elsa's Grand Princess Ball and need new dresses. We help create beautiful, sparkly outfits for the occasion. 
This video is for kids who love Disney Princesses and dress-up fun!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Playing Kitchen & Cooking Yummy Food for Gabby! 🍕🍰 | Gabby's Dollhouse Kitty Fairy Toys
videos.description: Kitty Fairy is sad Gabby can't come to her birthday party, so she makes her Play-Doh pizza, cupcakes, and cake to cheer her up. Join the fun with a toy kitchen playset in this pretend cooking adventure!
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: Peppa Pig Moves Into a Bigger Dollhouse! 🏠🐷  | Pretend Play
videos.description: Peppa Pig and her family have outgrown their toy home, so they’ve purchased a bigger new dollhouse! 🏠 Now Peppa and George can each have their own rooms.
videos.author: Yippee Toys

videos.title: A MINECRAFT MOVIE Trailer 2 (2025)
videos.description:
Watch the new trailer for A Minecraft Movie! In theaters April 4, 2025.

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn’t just help you craft, it’s essential to one’s survival! Four misfits—Garrett “The Garbage Man” Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)—find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they’ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative…the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world.

© Warner Bros. Pictures Germany

videos.title: Minions 2: The Rise of Gru - Scared Minions Sleep With Gru (2022)
videos.description:
Watch the new tv spots for Minions: The Rise of Gru, an animation movie starring Steve Carell, Pierre Coffin and Russell Brand. In theaters July 1, 2022.

In the heart of the 1970s, amid a flurry of feathered hair and flared jeans, Gru (Oscar® nominee Steve Carell) is growing up in the suburbs. A fanboy of a supervillain supergroup known as the Vicious 6, Gru hatches a plan to become evil enough to join them. Luckily, he gets some mayhem-making backup from his loyal followers, the Minions. Together, Kevin, Stuart, Bob, and Otto - a new Minion sporting braces and a desperate need to please - deploy their skills as they and Gru build their first lair, experiment with their first weapons and pull off their first missions. When the Vicious 6 oust their leader, legendary fighter Wild Knuckles, Gru interviews to become their newest member. It doesn’t go well (to say the least), and only gets worse after Gru outsmarts them and suddenly finds himself the mortal enemy of the apex of evil. On the run, Gru will turn to an unlikely source for guidance, Wild Knuckles himself, and discover that even bad guys need a little help from their friends. 

© Universal Pictures

The film finds Thor (Chris Hemsworth) on a journey unlike anything he’s ever faced – a quest for inner peace. But his retirement is interrupted by a galactic killer known as Gorr the God Butcher (Christian Bale), who seeks the extinction of the gods. To combat the threat, Thor enlists the help of King Valkyrie (Tessa Thompson), Korg (Taika Waititi) and ex-girlfriend Jane Foster (Natalie Portman), who – to Thor’s surprise – inexplicably wields his magical hammer, Mjolnir, as the Mighty Thor. Together, they embark upon a harrowing cosmic adventure to uncover the mystery of the God Butcher’s vengeance and stop him before it’s too late.
